{"tid":694710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[凶兆？]傳蘋果公司削新iPhone零件訂單　股價場外曾跌2%","createTime":"2018-06-08T14:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T06:37:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3863a1243eb0c5743fdca93ecc279e63ace33d","tid":694710,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，有傳蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)於2018年<span style=\"color: red;\">下半年iPhone零件供應將下跌20%</span>，拖累股價場外交易一度跌2%。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述零件供應鏈消息人士消息，指蘋果公司已削減訂單，並對今年iPhone付運量採取「謹慎策略」。<br />\n<br />\n據早前消息，蘋果公司將於今年下半年公布3款新iPhone型號，但該公司僅預期付運量約8,000萬部，與去年新iPhone型號付運量達1億部勁減兩成。若消息屬實，<span style=\"color: red;\">意味蘋果亦料新iPhone銷情不如去年。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蘋果公司未對消息置評。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180608/bkn-20180608210921555-0608_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180608%2Fbkn-20180608210921555-0608_00842_001.html&d=E4ILr%2BITO37y6XHO142KSRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9b6d68d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180608/bkn-20180608210921555-0608_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"af3379a805f46e35a4871169b21d6ea0f6f663e0","tid":694710,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司未對消息置評<br />\n蘋果公司未對消息置評<br />\n蘋果公司未對消息置評<br />\n蘋果公司未對消息置評<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmeans real<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca04797879f29d4ce9b1998349f3b49cfc8c2558","tid":694710,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"World No iphone"},{"pid":"95ec848ec34bb0c75856a87881539d92edccef1b","tid":694710,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"等緊蘋果上到一萬億市值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"